::

## 基础用法
::TuffCodeBlock{lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxTooltip content="复制成功">
      <TxButton variant="ghost">Copy</TxButton>
    </TxTooltip>
  </template>
---
:::

## Anchor 透传
::TuffCodeBlock{lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxTooltip
      content="底部提示"
      :anchor="{ placement: 'bottom', showArrow: true, panelBackground: 'mask' }"
    >
      <TxButton variant="ghost">Bottom</TxButton>
    </TxTooltip>
  </template>
---
:::

## API（简版）
::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: content
    type: 'string'
    default: "''"
    description: '提示内容'
  - name: trigger
    type: "'hover' | 'click' | 'focus'"
    default: "'hover'"
    description: '触发方式'
  - name: open-delay
    type: 'number'
    default: '200'
    description: '延迟显示（ms）'
  - name: close-delay
    type: 'number'
    default: '120'
    description: '延迟关闭（ms）'
  - name: interactive
    type: 'boolean'
    default: 'false'
    description: 'hover 模式下允许鼠标进入浮层'
  - name: max-height
    type: 'number'
    default: '320'
    description: '提示层最大高度'
  - name: anchor
    type: 'Partial<BaseAnchorProps>'
    default: '{}'
    description: '透传给 TxBaseAnchor 的配置（placement/showArrow/panelBackground 等）'
---
:::

## Design Notes
- 文案尽量短，避免多行提示。  
- 与触发元素的间距保持轻盈。
- 复杂外观和动效请通过 `anchor` 配置，不在 Tooltip 层重复抽象。

